F (C{(λa)b})

= C{a[b/]}

F (C{(λa)[s]})

= C{λa[⇑ (s)]}

F (C{(ab)[s]})

= C{a[s]b[s]}

F (C{1[a/]})

= C{a}

if a ∈ N Fυ

F (C{1[a/]})

= C{1[F (a)/]}

if a ∈/ N Fυ

F (C{(m + 1)[a/]}) = C{m}

if a ∈ N Fυ

F (C{(m + 1)[a/]}) = C{(m + 1)[F (a)/]} if a ∈/ N Fυ

F (C{1[⇑ (s)]})

= C{1}

if s ∈ N Fυ

F (C{1[⇑ (s)]})

= C{1[⇑ (F (s))]}

if s ∈/ N Fυ

F (C{(m + 1)[⇑ (s)]}) = C{m[s][↑]}

if s ∈ N Fυ

F (C{(m + 1)[⇑ (s)]}) = C{(m + 1)[⇑ (F (s))]} if s ∈/ N Fυ

F (C{m[↑]})

= C{m + 1}

