n⇑(n)

=0

n⇑(ab) = n⇑(a) + n⇑(b)

n⇑(a[s]) = n⇑(a) + n⇑(s)

n⇑(⇑ (s)) = n⇑(s) + 1

n⇑(a/) = n⇑(a) n⇑(λa) = n⇑(a) n⇑(↑) = 0

n⇑(n)

=0

n⇑(ab)

= n⇑(a) + n⇑(b)

n⇑(a[⇑k (b/)]) = n⇑(a) + n⇑(b) + k

n⇑(λa)

= n⇑(a)

n⇑(a[⇑k (↑)]) = n⇑(a) + k

ÓÖ a ∈ Λtυ Û Ò Ø ÒÙÑ Ö Ó × Ø× Ò a¸ ÛÖ ØØ Ò n↑(a)¸ Ò Ø ÜÔ Ø Û Ý

n↑(n)

=0

n↑(ab) = n↑(a) + n↑(b)

n↑(a[s]) = n↑(a) + n↑(s)

n↑(⇑ (s)) = n↑(s)

n↑(a/) = n↑(a) n↑(λa) = n↑(a) n↑(↑) = 1

¾¾

ÓÖ ÕÙ Ú Ð ÒØÐÝ

n↑(n)

=0

n↑(ab)

= n↑(a) + n↑(b)

n↑(a[⇑k (b/)]) = n↑(a) + n↑(b)

n↑(λa)

= n↑(a)

n↑(a[⇑k (↑)]) = n↑(a) + 1

